  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Lost Gallery is a horror game in which you are a phantom thief with the aim of stealing artwork from an exhibition. Survive the insane art and make off with as many hidden treasures as you can.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >You Are a Master Thief:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you find a valuable work, you can steal it instantly by touching it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990080/extras/2026d99b3313bf22a34cf66d40e36f67.poster.avif?t=1742862004\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990080/extras/2026d99b3313bf22a34cf66d40e36f67.webm?t=1742862004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990080/extras/2026d99b3313bf22a34cf66d40e36f67.mp4?t=1742862004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Using the Crowbar:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even the most carefully guarded pieces can be obtained easily using a crowbar. Remember that danger is always looming, so stay aware of your surroundings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990080/extras/4c9939edbeb350cd94ac9eb2c9b31c64.poster.avif?t=1742862004\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990080/extras/4c9939edbeb350cd94ac9eb2c9b31c64.webm?t=1742862004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990080/extras/4c9939edbeb350cd94ac9eb2c9b31c64.mp4?t=1742862004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Playtime:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1-2 hours </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Autosave System:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game will automatically save at certain points.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Controls:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move: WASD</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run: LSHIFT</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move Camera: Mouse</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Options: ESC</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump: Space</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact: E</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take Out / Put Away Crowbar: Right Click</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use Crowbar: Left Click</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to the Secret Exhibition:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A popular exhibition is shut down immediately after a bizarre incident occurred in which people were murdered by the works on display. At the same time, you – a phantom thief – are inside stealing priceless works of art from this chaotic exhibition. All that's left is to escape. However, when you accidentally discover a hidden door leading to a secret exhibition your plan takes a turn for the worse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990080/extras/bea65ed7e4fcd860c63cddd568dcd771.poster.avif?t=1742862004\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990080/extras/bea65ed7e4fcd860c63cddd568dcd771.webm?t=1742862004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990080/extras/bea65ed7e4fcd860c63cddd568dcd771.mp4?t=1742862004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Regarding Posting, Livestreaming, Etc. of Gameplay Videos:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No permission is needed. The Lost Gallery allows the posting and livestreaming of gameplay videos as well as the monetization associated with it.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Lost Gallery is a horror game in which you are a phantom thief with the aim of stealing artwork from an exhibition. Survive the insane art and make off with as many hidden treasures as you can.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >You Are a Master Thief:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you find a valuable work, you can steal it instantly by touching it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990080/extras/2026d99b3313bf22a34cf66d40e36f67.poster.avif?t=1742862004\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990080/extras/2026d99b3313bf22a34cf66d40e36f67.webm?t=1742862004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990080/extras/2026d99b3313bf22a34cf66d40e36f67.mp4?t=1742862004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Using the Crowbar:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even the most carefully guarded pieces can be obtained easily using a crowbar. Remember that danger is always looming, so stay aware of your surroundings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990080/extras/4c9939edbeb350cd94ac9eb2c9b31c64.poster.avif?t=1742862004\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990080/extras/4c9939edbeb350cd94ac9eb2c9b31c64.webm?t=1742862004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990080/extras/4c9939edbeb350cd94ac9eb2c9b31c64.mp4?t=1742862004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Playtime:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1-2 hours </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Autosave System:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game will automatically save at certain points.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Controls:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move: WASD</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run: LSHIFT</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move Camera: Mouse</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Options: ESC</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump: Space</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact: E</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take Out / Put Away Crowbar: Right Click</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use Crowbar: Left Click</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to the Secret Exhibition:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A popular exhibition is shut down immediately after a bizarre incident occurred in which people were murdered by the works on display. At the same time, you – a phantom thief – are inside stealing priceless works of art from this chaotic exhibition. All that's left is to escape. However, when you accidentally discover a hidden door leading to a secret exhibition your plan takes a turn for the worse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990080/extras/bea65ed7e4fcd860c63cddd568dcd771.poster.avif?t=1742862004\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990080/extras/bea65ed7e4fcd860c63cddd568dcd771.webm?t=1742862004\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990080/extras/bea65ed7e4fcd860c63cddd568dcd771.mp4?t=1742862004\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Regarding Posting, Livestreaming, Etc. of Gameplay Videos:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No permission is needed. The Lost Gallery allows the posting and livestreaming of gameplay videos as well as the monetization associated with it.</p>",
